description:
Tainted is a psychological horror tale set in a supernatural background. It is a look at the tortured mind of a human being who questions if his actions are conducted by the loss of his sanity or by something much much worse.

Edward stands accused of a violent massacre at a diner. Having no recollection of the events, he insists on his innocence. The problem: he can't clean the blood stains from his hands and the voices in his head won't stop.
name: Tainted

description:
An awesome comic about heroes, wizards, monsters, magic and lulz. You've reached your "Saving Point".

An ancient statuette containing the power of the world's oldest enemy has been stolen! Follow Bolaf and his band of underdogs as they embark on a journey that will change their lives...in every sense of the word!

Created with love by the artistic husband and wife team of Samuel Figueroa and Rangely García; "Saving Point" is an action/adventure/comedy story set in a fantasy world that breathes classic RPG game elements.

If you ever wondered why do monsters turn into items when killed, why random encounters just don't happen inside towns or if people get pissed when heroes just barge into their house and steal their possessions, well...all we gotta say is:
It's dangerous to go alone! Take this comic with you!

"Saving Point"
Story: Rangely García & Samuel Figueroa
Art: Rangely García
Originally published by: RBA Comics
name: Saving Point
